body_html: Please provide details about what platform you are using (operating system, architecture). Also include your TensorFlow version. Also, include what model you are trying to train and how your invoking it, moving it to another machine, etc.. We ask for this in the issue submission template, because it is really difficult to help without that information. Thanks!
